credits that were needed.
Mr Ulf Dinkelspiel, the Swedish trade minister, said yesterday that the
government was considering whether to ease the existing restrictions but he
could give no timetable of when they were likely to be abolished.
The new deal for the Guangdong mobile telephone network will be implemented
during the first quarter of next year, Ericsson said.
