powerful and influential strategist, Senator Graham Richardson, reports
Emilia Tagaza in Canberra.
The reshuffle, though minor, is another setback for Mr Keating. One of the
ministerial posts was filled by someone who is likely to unseat another of
his staunchest supporters in parliament, the Speaker of the House of
Representatives, Mr Leo McLeay.
The new minister for consumer affairs, Miss Jeanette McHugh, has represented
