offshore finance at the South African bank's disposal.
He said this would bring the total of Middle East banks ready to do business
with ABSA Bank to around 40.
Gulf states have not formally lifted sanctions against South Africa but
deals which took place for years are gathering momentum as apartheid is
dismantled.
