<HEADLINE>
FT  26 MAY 92 / World News In Brief: Philippine fast ends
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Philippine presidential contender Miriam Santiago, heeding appeals from
Roman Catholic leaders, ended her three-day fast against alleged election
fraud.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
International Page 1
</PAGE>
</DOC>
