FT  26 MAY 92 / World News In Brief: Barcelona bombs
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Barcelona's Olympic security chiefs were on red alert after a bomb hidden in
a garbage bag exploded, injuring 15 people. A second bomb was detonated
outside government offices.
